## Envision – Flame-Retardant (FR) & Arc-Resistant (AR) Clothing

### Flame-Retardant (FR) Clothing

- Resists ignition and self-extinguishes when exposed to flame
- Protects against flash fires, open flames, welding sparks, and combustible dust

### Arc-Resistant (AR) Clothing

- Withstands extreme arc-flash heat and blast pressure
- Carries a calorie rating showing how much energy the garment can absorb before causing burns
- Always FR, but FR clothing alone is not automatically arc-rated.

**Comparison Table:**

| Attribute | FR Clothing | AR Clothing |
|-----------|-------------|-------------|
| Protects against flames & flash fire | ✓ | ✓ |
| Protects against arc flash | ✗ | ✓ |
| Always arc-rated? | ✗ | ✓ |
| Always flame-resistant? | ✓ | ✓ |

