## Envision's Equipment & Facilities Optimization

Envision maintains an in-house equipment and facilities optimization team consisting of one manager and five technicians, each with expertise in their assigned departments. This structure supports a robust preventative maintenance program that has measurably improved equipment reliability and uptime. The team works closely with department managers and BVI employees to optimize workflows through programmable equipment, process templates, and tailored adjustments that address specific operational needs.

